<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今天的突破性故事|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com是您最新的中国新闻报道和时事的在线来源</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 09 Feb 2025 15:14:48 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国的健康监管机构捍卫当地仿制药的质量</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-health-regulator-defends-quality-local-generic-drugs-2025-02-09/</link><description>周日，中国的医疗保健监管机构捍卫了它已批准通过该国公立医院分发的非应有药物的功效，称对质量关注的调查发现它们是未经证实的。</description><pubDate>Sun, 09 Feb 2025 13:27:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-health-regulator-defends-quality-local-generic-drugs-2025-02-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国公司详细介绍了DeepSeek Frenzy的AI使用</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/amid-deepseek-frenzy-chinese-companies-detail-use-ai-2025-02-09/</link><description>它的平台刺激了爱国呼吁中国资产估值更高的呼吁。</description><pubDate>Sun, 09 Feb 2025 11:57:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/amid-deepseek-frenzy-chinese-companies-detail-use-ai-2025-02-09/</guid></item><item><title>繁荣后，中国要恢复清洁能源补贴</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/china-roll-back-clean-power-subsidies-after-boom-2025-02-09/</link><description>中国最高的经济规划局周日表示，在太阳能和风能设施繁荣时，正在采取措施缩减可再生能源项目的补贴。</description><pubDate>Sun, 09 Feb 2025 07:29:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/china-roll-back-clean-power-subsidies-after-boom-2025-02-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国的消费者通货膨胀率达到5个月，生产商通货膨胀率仍然存在</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-consumer-inflation-quickens-january-producer-deflation-persists-2025-02-09/</link><description>中国的消费通货膨胀率在一月份的五个月内加速到最快，而生产商价格通货膨胀持续存在，反映了消费者支出混合和工厂活动疲软。</description><pubDate>Sun, 09 Feb 2025 01:52:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-consumer-inflation-quickens-january-producer-deflation-persists-2025-02-09/</guid></item><item><title>台湾派遣官员给我们讨论可能的特朗普关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/taiwan-sends-officials-us-discuss-possible-trump-tariffs-2025-02-08/</link><description>台湾经济部长Kuo Jyh-Huei周六表示，台湾已将官员派往华盛顿，讨论唐纳德·特朗普总统可能的美国关税，并在施加的情况下做准备。</description><pubDate>Sat, 08 Feb 2025 07:54:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/taiwan-sends-officials-us-discuss-possible-trump-tariffs-2025-02-08/</guid></item><item><title>中国敦促巴拿马在宣布带和公路出口后“做出正确的决定”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-urges-panama-make-right-decision-after-announcing-belt-road-exit-2025-02-08/</link><description>中国周六对巴拿马打算离开北京的腰带和道路倡议表示遗憾，敦促拉丁美洲国家“做出正确的决定”。</description><pubDate>Sat, 08 Feb 2025 03:37:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-urges-panama-make-right-decision-after-announcing-belt-road-exit-2025-02-08/</guid></item><item><title>中国副总理将参加巴黎AI峰会</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/chinese-vice-premier-set-attend-paris-ai-summit-2025-02-07/</link><description>外交部周五表示，中国副总理张盖奎宁将于2月12日至2月12日在AI行动峰会上担任习近平总统的特别代表。</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Feb 2025 08:56:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/chinese-vice-premier-set-attend-paris-ai-summit-2025-02-07/</guid></item><item><title>香港向美国关税决定向世贸组织投诉</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/hong-kong-complain-wto-us-tariff-decision-2025-02-07/</link><description>香港周五表示，将向世界贸易组织（WTO）提出投诉，要求美国决定对亚洲金融枢纽的商品征收10％的关税，因为美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）以中国进口为目标。</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Feb 2025 08:27:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/hong-kong-complain-wto-us-tariff-decision-2025-02-07/</guid></item><item><title>中国一月的银行贷款飙升，但需求仍然脆弱：路透社民意调查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-january-bank-lending-seen-surging-demand-still-fragile-2025-02-07/</link><description>路透社的一项民意调查显示，与12月相比，中国的新人民币贷款可能在1月份飙升，但仍低于一年前的创纪录水平。</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Feb 2025 06:21:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-january-bank-lending-seen-surging-demand-still-fragile-2025-02-07/</guid></item><item><title>泰国领导人吸引中国游客，她说她“中国血液”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/wooing-chinese-tourists-thai-leader-says-she-has-chinese-blood-her-2025-02-07/</link><description>泰国总理寻求在访问泰国的中国游客中解决安全问题，他说她“中国血”，她亲自研究了安全方案，以确保中国公民的安全。</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Feb 2025 05:31:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/wooing-chinese-tourists-thai-leader-says-she-has-chinese-blood-her-2025-02-07/</guid></item><item><title>香港邮政继续将包裹暂停到美国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/hongkong-post-continue-suspend-parcels-us-2025-02-06/</link><description>香港邮政周四末表示，尽管美国邮政局（USPS）撤销了暂停来自中国和香港的包裹的决定，但仍将继续将邮政暂停到美国。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 18:32:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/hongkong-post-continue-suspend-parcels-us-2025-02-06/</guid></item><item><title>欧洲委员会要求Shein提供有关非法商品的信息</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/european-commission-asks-chinas-shein-information-illegal-content-goods-2025-02-06/</link><description>欧盟高管周四表示，欧盟委员会已要求在线快速时尚零售商Shein提供内部文件，并提供有关与市场上非法商品和内容有关的风险的更详细信息。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 11:23:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/european-commission-asks-chinas-shein-information-illegal-content-goods-2025-02-06/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-gas-traders-seek-tariff-waivers-beijing-us-imports-sources-say-2025-02-06/</link><description>贸易消息人士周四表示，石油和天然气商人可能会从2月10日起对中国政府计划对美国原油和液化天然气进口的北京的关税寻求豁免。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 10:53:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-gas-traders-seek-tariff-waivers-beijing-us-imports-sources-say-2025-02-06/</guid></item><item><title>阿斯利康首席执行官说，公司无法接触王，在中国被拘留</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/astrazeneca-ceo-says-company-has-no-access-executive-wang-detention-china-2025-02-06/</link><description>其首席执行官周四表示，中国当局已经对阿斯利康进行了几次调查，以调查其对制药商前高级主管Leon Wang的调查，并根据需要提供信息。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 10:10:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/astrazeneca-ceo-says-company-has-no-access-executive-wang-detention-china-2025-02-06/</guid></item><item><title>DeepSeek发烧燃料中国人工智能股票的爱国赌注</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/deepseek-fever-fuels-patriotic-bets-chinese-ai-stocks-2025-02-06/</link><description>中国投资者正在赶紧与AI相关的股票，押注本土初创公司DeepSeek的人工智能进步将导致该行业的繁荣，并在一场加强的中国技术战争中向中国发动了主动性。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 08:14:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/deepseek-fever-fuels-patriotic-bets-chinese-ai-stocks-2025-02-06/</guid></item></channel></rss>